DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260711T083000
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=FR
SUMMARY:PAYDAY — Send $1200 to wife. Text AI: paid $___
DESCRIPTION:1. Transfer payment from YOUR account\n2. Log in phone check-in app\n3. Text AI: paid $[amount]\n\nRamp if needed: wk1 $600 / wk2 $900 / wk3+ $1200
